title: VA - Funky Day Pass [2008] 2 CDs 70s Rockers Funk It Up
description:
From Bowie to Deep Purple - from T-Rex to Led Zeppelin - from Nazareth to the Eagles - at one point or another every self respecting artist in the Seventies tried their hand at a bit of Funk. The results were suprisingly satisfying ... Check this out, I think you&#039;ll enjoy!

Keep it going for as long as possible so that others get to listen.
